<h3>Radiation and Cloudiness</h3>
<br><br>
<br><br>
Solar radiation in January was below average in most of Europe (Figure 17). In line with this, cloud cover was above average in most of Europe (Figure 18). An exception is Norway, where not only precipitation but also cloud cover was below normal.
